                     <interp inst="t17801018-15-off79" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing a pair of linen sheets, value 10 s. a woollen blanket, value 2 s. a linen curtain, value 2 s. and a flat-iron, value 6 d. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17801018-15-victim204" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Lowe
                        <interp inst="t17801018-15-victim204" type="surname" value="Lowe"></interp>
